Diagnosis and Symptoms Checklist

Source: R/data.R
ADSXLIST.Rd

Diagnosis and Symptoms Checklist data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(ADSXLIST)

Format

A data frame with 4884 observations and 40 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with factor levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 2407

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • VISDATE Date Registry EXAMDATE on matching VISCODE Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AXNAUSEA character 1. Nausea 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXVOMIT character 2. Vomiting 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXDIARRH character 3. Diarrhea 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXCONSTP character 4. Constipation 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXABDOMN character 5. Abdominal discomfort 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXSWEATN character 6. Sweating 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXDIZZY character 7. Dizziness 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXENERGY character 8. Low energy 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXDROWSY character 9. Drowsiness 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXVISION character 10. Blurred vision 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXHDACHE character 11. Headache 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXDRYMTH character 12. Dry mouth 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXBREATH character 13. Shortness of breath 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXCOUGH character 14. Coughing 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXPALPIT character 15. Palpitations 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXCHEST character 16. Chest pain 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXURNDIS character 17. Urinary discomfort (e.g., burning) 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXURNFRQ character 18. Urinary frequency 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXANKLE character 19. Ankle swelling 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXMUSCLE character 20. Muscloskeletal pain 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXRASH character 21. Rash 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXINSOMN character 22. Insomnia 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXDPMOOD character 23. Depressed mood 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXCRYING character 24. Crying 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXELMOOD character 25. Elevated mood 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXWANDER character 26. Wandering 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXFALL character 27. Fall 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • AXOTHER character 28. Other/Diagnosis 1=Absent; 2=Present Decoded Value: Yes

  • ID numeric Range value: 2, ..., 8410

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 1, ..., 127

  • USERDATE Date Date record created Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 Date Date record last updated Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • update_stamp POSIXct POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
